sets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，少接觸唔記得正常"},{"pid":"9d2b508545f93ea443cdb432a2fc7ced762ee4c6","tid":192713,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:17:26.000Z","msg":"食左呢隻抗生素屙尿係會咁<br />\n我都試過<br />\n醫生應該要講定"},{"pid":"736eeaf925c850c5d7bca0fc22b50ee2b1358cbf","tid":192713,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"咁既顏色唔係應該係等於排返d藥物出黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食維他命B都會屙螢光黃色既尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似highlight筆d色咁<br />\n但維他命黎講 咁就等於排返多餘 身體唔吸收既維他命<br />\n不過樓主隻藥係唔係咁就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係講下 留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04155884785e3fc7ce7892c413c8319131fdb02a","tid":192713,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>血尿唔喺咁<br />\n<br />\nBTW樓主有無聽過香港有  急症室？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲尿一日以上都咁深色  睇下醫生好</blockquote><br />\n佢今晚先同我講。。但又診所關晒門，佢又唔想睇急症(老人家習性覺得貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾舊水貴得去邊  住院就一百蚊一日  急症就二百二 <br />\n衰啲講句   如果腎有事  你估止唔止住兩日丫啦？<br />\n<br />\n同上面位巴打講嘅一樣   飲多啲水<br />\n情況都喺咁嘅就去A&amp;E啦   另外  有無兩邊腰有無痛？"},{"pid":"59d72b11abc8ab34ebeb69a4326e155240511b69","tid":192713,"uid":79758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁似尿道炎食個隻止痛藥既色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果咁既色，應該有粒糖藥裝，圓形既藥。你睇下有冇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/09/021752_3d4be1b75a70fda278c453850b1d2864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F09%2F021752_3d4be1b75a70fda278c453850b1d2864.jpg&h=bb663e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時就係呢D"},{"pid":"b9bb1b629c9ee5b71a71856d03760b3728ff604c","tid":192713,"uid":12714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Amoxy唔會令尿液染色，咁紅嘅好可能係gross hematuria，成因好多(e.g. 腎石、尿道炎、trauma)<br />\nAmoxy引致gross hematuria淨係揾到一個case: <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1026727/pdf/westjmed00130-0076c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC1026727%2Fpdf%2Fwestjmed00130-0076c.pdf&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e0365196\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1026727/pdf/westjmed00130-0076c.pdf</a><br />\nConclusion: 唔似amoxy引起。快啲去睇醫生!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n利申Medic仔</blockquote><br />\n佢痾左落馬桶 睇唔清<br />\nBtw 唔似gross hameturia<br />\n似tea color 多啲"},{"pid":"506cd8b916a80c904f44a7ab3a28c73cf6d2914f","tid":192713,"uid":103519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁似尿道炎食個隻止痛藥既色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nys exact7ly <br />\nrifampin?</blockquote><br />\n個隻叫pyridium<br />\nRifa 通常醫tb ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw<br />\n樓主痾到去馬桶 好難睇得清<br />\n似似地tea color<br />\n個人有冇黃到？ <br />\n建議去急症室睇</blockquote><br />\ntea colour --&gt; rhabdo? if rhabdo should have mental changes already<br />\nJaundice --&gt; hepatitis? why suspect from abnormal urine coour<br />\n<br />\nPyridium colour more orange-red or orange-yellow. This looks like gross hematuria to me<br />\n<br />\nAnyhow, visit emergency dept asap"},{"pid":"eff7bbc8d93122f7ebbf27111f89388a4b6b3340","tid":192713,"uid":103519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Amoxy唔會令尿液染